6897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466897</a>"},{"pid":"82c0eef6a6acd50495f105f33ae130d4fab04e4c","tid":1466381,"uid":56802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n既然知道對方有卧底 輿論戰就應該捉住呢點spin<br />\n黑二哥絕對無可能公開卧底細節 機場嘅事就係卧底做 而家黑警無公信力 好多人自然會信有卧底講法"},{"pid":"625e378537b8b8fc9345218e455f2ee2b5b10e55","tid":1466381,"uid":104378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9e91353e5666f011bb6b5999554a435db5c2f9d6","tid":1466381,"uid":266491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b1c9c4c567dd385aa7233c0d6fa86e18e88f99","tid":1466381,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"Stay tgt"},{"pid":"90eee39c4796d8f954ce402fa3f4b22258b42d26","tid":1466381,"uid":178731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"勿忘初衷, 五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n全香港都係我哋表達聲音嘅地方！<br />\n兄弟爬山, BE WATER"},{"pid":"2a37c8a93aa60abd8578eb4d5badf183b8915898","tid":1466381,"uid":236234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76a14549fb54b0ffc44a8bfe66abacd68b7e5ed6","tid":1466381,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:18.000Z","msg":"今晚<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又打記者又打醫護又打公安</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中計撚又話中哂計又成 屌講真就算真係自己人走哂<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剩返前排係鬼唔肯走</span></span></strong> 中計撚一樣話我地中計 永遠立於不敗之地<br />\n<br />\n點解唔積極d 諗下聽日輿論戰點準備<br />\n<br />\n琴日既popo記招 二哥剩係話喬裝 但根本就無回應過派左幾多人 幾時會&lsquo;喬裝&rsquo; 而佢地到底有無<strong>&lsquo;煽動暴力&rsquo;</strong> 都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>popo自說自話</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n既然係咁 點解唔索性用機場單野對準返popo喬裝件事 就算佢死都唔認 都只會更加突顯到佢混入呢件事係<span style=\"